snippet.title: Inferno 2 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The ultimate twin-stick action-RPG/shooter is here! 
Launches September 19 on Nintendo Switch, PS4 and Xbox One.
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/inferno-2-switch/
https://store.playstation.com/es-es/product/EP1245-CUSA12285_00-0000000000000001
https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/inferno-2/9n2pzsk8llpp?activetab=pivot:overviewtab

For more information, visit:
http://www.2awesomestudio.com/press/sheet.php?p=Inferno_2
